r with two young boys. The Prophet gave one of them to Ali ibn Abi Talib, and he said, \u201cDo not beat him. I have prohibited hitting the people of prayer, and I saw him praying.\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/16\/prophet-frees-slaves-taif\/","url_meta":{"origin":38347,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet frees the slaves of al-Ta&#8217;if","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, besieged the people of Al-Ta\u2019if, he freed their slaves who came out to him. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 3257 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0635\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36084,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/10\/no-entry-injustice\/","url_meta":{"origin":38347,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Iqtisas: No heavenly entry until wrongs are righted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah will gather the servants naked, uncircumcised, and destitute.\u201d We said, \u201cWhat is destitute?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey will have nothing with them. They will be addressed with a voice heard from afar: I am\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":684,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/08\/prophet-never-said-uff\/","url_meta":{"origin":38347,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Manners: The Prophet never even said &#8216;Uff&#8217;","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I served the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, for ten years. By Allah, he never even said to me, \u201cUff!\u201d He never said harshly, \u201cWhy did you do that?\u201d or, \u201cWhy did you not do that?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2309 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28834,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/hasan-husayn-two-sweet-basils\/","url_meta":{"origin":38347,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Husayn: Hasan and Husayn are my two sweet-basils","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Nu\u2019m reported: I watched Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, as he was asked about a man killing mosquitoes. Ibn Umar said, \u201cWhere are you from?\u201d The man said, \u201cThe people of Iraq.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cLook at this man! He asks me about killing mosquitoes\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38347","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=38347"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38347\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=38347"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=38347"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=38347"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}